-- Czech National Bank Grants Mobile-Payments License, HN Reports
-- B y   L e n k a   P o n i k e l s k a
-- 2012-05-21T07:21:40Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-05-21/czech-national-bank-grants-mobile-payments-license-hn-reports.html
The Czech National Bank granted a
license for payments via mobile phones to Mopet CZ, a Czech
joint venture of three mobile operators and banks,  Hospodarske
Noviny  reported, citing Mopet spokeswoman Vendula Volakova.  The service, called Mobito, will encompass online payments
or money transfers and should start during the third quarter,
the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Lenka Ponikelska in Prague at 
 lponikelska1@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
James M. Gomez at 
 jagomez@bloomberg.net  